Title: 97 Seconds
Plot: The candidates are now two teams of five women and five men, competing on diagnosing and treating a wheelchair-bound man. Meanwhile House does experiments on himself to test what happens after death, and Foreman, at another hospital, is treating his team in a House-like manner.
GuestStars: Brian Klugman, Meera Simhan, Melinda Dahl, Caitlin Dahl, Charlie Hofheimer, Kathleen York, Mary Kate Schellhardt, Reynaldo Rosales, Douglas Spain
